<p>You. Are. Over-designing. Look at this. It's a nice website. Why do you need to animate a trendy banner flag when I hover over it? You spent hours on it and added 80 kilobytes to your site, and some visitor using an iPad with fat fingers will never see that. Not to mention blind people will never see that, but they don't see any of your content.</p>
