<h2>This is a website. Look at it. You've never seen one before.</h2>
// ... existing code ...
<p>Like a man who's never grown out his beard has no idea what his true natural state is, you have no idea what a website is. All you have ever seen are bastardizations of what should be text communicating a message. This is a real, naked website. Look at it. It's beautiful.</p>
